        },
        "committer": {
          "name": "Vitaly Fertman",
          "email": "vitaly_fertman@xyratex.com",
          "date": "2013-01-31 13:21:47.000000000",
          "tz": 240
        },
        "subject": "LU-2722 clio: directIO thread races with completion thread",
        "message": "LU-2722 clio: directIO thread races with completion thread\n\nll_direct_IO_26()) ASSERTION( obj->cob_transient_pages == 0 ) failed\n\nThe directio thread puts pages to the transfer in osc_io_submit(), and\nwaits for its completion. Upon completion, osc_completion() is called,\nwhich notifies waiters IO is completed and only after that put the\npage. the original directIO thread wakes up and may succeed to assert\non the last page which is not yet put by osc_completion().\n\nSigned-off-by: Vitaly Fertman <vitaly_fertman@xyratex.com>\nChange-Id: Ib912e913885a9ff2cb1e9c865ae2003a676c2b5b\nXyratex-bug-id: MRP-838\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
